text: Air Seychelles is the national airline of Seychelles. It started in 1978. In 1983, it began international flights to Frankfurt and London. Its head office is at Seychelles International Airport on the island of Mahé."Offices & GSAs head Office ." Air Seychelles. Retrieved on 29 January 2011 "Head Office Air Seychelles Ltd Head Office International Airport P.O.Box 386 Victoria, Mahé, Seychelles." As of 2015, Air Seychelles flies to 10 cities and has 10 airplanes. ==References== Category:Airlines of Africa Category:Organizations based in Seychelles Category:1977 establishments in Africa
